        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''People don't talk about war like they did when I was a child. But every now and then, you stop to think that Seoul could be destroyed in a matter of minutes. I have a family, and that is no way to have to live.''</p>
        <p>PARK KIL TAE, a South Korean. [A12]</p>
      </block>
